The paper proposes a method to enhance localization accuracy in dynamic connected vehicle networks, which involves the use of communication and information exchange between vehicles. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves the use of robotics and control systems, which suggests the possibility of cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves the use of cooperative systems, which suggests the possibility of cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves the use of information theory, which suggests the possibility of cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper involves the use of computer vision techniques, which suggests the possibility of cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
